#--------------Bootstraping---------------------
listofdfs <- list()


for (i in c(7:13)){
  alg.data %>% 
  filter(alg.data[,i]>=1)%>% 
  mutate(Topic = colnames(alg.data)[i])%>% 
    sample_n(size = 100)%>% 
    group_by( VADERclass, Topic) %>% 
  
  summarise(Sent = n()) ->listofdfs[[i]]
}
bootstrap<- bind_rows(listofdfs)

bootstrap<- 
  bootstrap %>% 
  group_by(Topic) %>% 
  mutate(All = sum(Sent),percent=(100*Sent/All))
